<p><b>Using our services</b><br>
We provide a range of telecommunications products and services. To provide you with these products and services and bill you accurately, we need to collect and store some of your personal information. We also use some of your information to develop new products and services so that we better tailor our offers to your needs.</p>
<p><b>Privacy in the digital world</b><br>
To help you understand privacy and security in the digital world we offer information and advice about&nbsp;online safety&nbsp;and&nbsp;data security. We are also developing more tools to allow you to control your own privacy settings.</p>
<p><b>Want to know more?</b><br>
Millions of people across Australia trust us with their personal information. We continue to work diligently every day to honour your trust. To find out more about how we manage and use your personal information we encourage you to read our&nbsp;<a href="https://www.telstra.com.au/privacy/privacy-statement">Privacy Statement</a>.</p>
